    "Dictionary": {
        "Entries": {
            "zh-cn": {

"kojo_default_com_interaction_talk_accept_failure_1":"\"嗯……是啊，挺好的。\"$self$说着却目光飘忽，明显没在听。",
"kojo_default_com_interaction_talk_accept_failure_2":"\"所以……你到底想说什么？\"$self$微微歪头，语气中带着一丝不耐。",
"kojo_default_com_interaction_talk_accept_failure_3":"\"嗯……大概吧。\"$self$含糊地回应，看起来只是想快点结束话题。",
"kojo_default_com_interaction_talk_accept_success_1":"\"真的假的？太搞笑了吧！\"$self$笑出声来",
"kojo_default_com_interaction_talk_accept_success_2":"$self$：\"「你讲得挺有意思的，不继续了吗？\""

            },
            "en-us": {

"kojo_default_com_interaction_talk_accept_failure_1":"\"Uh-huh… yeah. Sounds great.\" $self$ glances at something else mid-conversation, clearly tuned out.",
"kojo_default_com_interaction_talk_accept_failure_2":"\"Is there a point to this, or…?\" $self$ tilts her head slightly, impatience creeping into her tone.",
"kojo_default_com_interaction_talk_accept_failure_3":"\"Mmm… I guess.\" $self$ replies vaguely, clearly just trying to end the topic.",
"kojo_default_com_interaction_talk_accept_success_1":"\"Wait, seriously? That’s hilarious.\" $self$ laughs out loud",
"kojo_default_com_interaction_talk_accept_success_2":"$self$: \"You’ve got good stories. Not gonna keep going?\""


                
            }
